- If `x₁ ≠ x₂`, then the slope `s = (y₂ - y₁) / (x₂ - x₁)`. The sum point `R = P + Q` has coordinates `x₃ = s² + a₁s - a₂ - x₁ - x₂` and `y₃ = s(x₁ - x₃) - y₁ - a₁x₃ - a₃`.

